    • Field Detail

      • DEFAULT

        public static final RelMetadataFixture DEFAULT
        Default fixture.

        Use this, or call the withXxx methods to make one with the properties you need. Fixtures are immutable, so whatever your test does to this fixture, it won't break other tests.
